Introduction:
	This Apache Camel component allows you to create Camel routes from and to Progress Apama correlators.

Requirements:
	Java 6 required.

Build instructions:
	Import the following jar files into your local maven repository:

	File -> groupId / artifactId / version / packaging
	APAMA_HOME/lib/engine_client4.2.jar -> com.progress.apama / engine-client / 4.2 / jar
	APAMA_HOME/lib/util4.2.jar -> com.progress.apama / util / 4.2 / jar

	Now use maven to package the jarfile:

	mvn clean package

